<br>
I have always felt there is something a bit McCarthyist about select committee hearings. Of course the MP’s and spin-doctors love this sort of publicity but to drag a mild mannered 60-year-old (well almost) academic into the full glare of media publicity and then publicly humiliate him is a bit much.<br>
<br>
